      }
    },
    {
      "id": "https://uofa.net/synth/validation/vr-mesh-sensitivity",
      "type": "ValidationResult",
      "name": "Mesh sensitivity and discretization convergence study",
      "description": "Richardson extrapolation applied to three systematically refined meshes (1.2 M, 4.8 M, 19.2 M cells). Grid convergence index (GCI) computed for NIH and peak wall shear stress. Coarse-to-fine GCI below 3.1% for all QoIs. Study treated as a deterministic verification activity; no stochastic UQ loop applied to this result specifically, as boundary conditions are held fixed at nominal values for convergence assessment purposes."
    },
